{{Quote|I was just one of a team of extras who worked on the Star Wars films. There was a hard core team of about 15 of us who worked continually on the films as different characters (mostly with masks or helmets on) who were then added to when there were larger scenes such as the massed guard of honour on the Death Star. We spent most of our time running around the sets as Stormtroopers , standing guard at doors or following Darth Vader around. In addition to Stormtroopers and Rebel Soldiers I also played a number of 'masked' Aliens.|Richard Bonehill|<ref name="Bonehill personal site" />}}
'''Richard Bonehill''' was an actor who played character extras in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']], the second and third films of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[original trilogy]].

==Biography==
Actor Richard Bonehill appeared in the final two films of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[original trilogy]], primarily playing masked background extras.<ref name="Convention-Guests">{{WebCite|url=http://www.convention-guests.com/html/richard_bonehill.html|text=Richard Bonehill|work=Convention-Guests|archivedate=20100411072040}} See also [http://www.convention-guests.com/assets/images/Richard-Bonehill-ESB.jpg image].</ref> Bonehill worked on [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']] for three weeks and [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']] for six weeks.<ref name="Bonehill personal site">{{WebCite|url=http://goo.gl/k6gEK|text=Star Wars|author=Bonehill, Richard|work=Bonehill - Richard and Lynne Bonehill's website|nolive=1|archiveurl=http://archive.vn/Qe7YN}}</ref> Although uncredited for any of his roles in either film, Bonehill is noted for playing a [[Cold assault stormtrooper|snowtrooper]], a [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]], and [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] officer [[Palo Torshan]] in ''The Empire Strikes Back''; and a stormtrooper, a [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]], an [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]], a [[TIE pilot]], and named characters [[Nien Nunb/Legends|Nien Nunb]], [[Ree-Yees/Legends|Ree-Yees]], and [[Mosep Binneed]] in ''Return of the Jedi''.<ref name="Convention-Guests" />

